{"title":"红船","authors":["李舟"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":6,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两片清纯的桨叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在南湖上青果般摇荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我慕名而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在心灵的颤栗中与你相遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年的夏天很热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几个紧皱眉头的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为火热的中国忧虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从上海那间屋子出来后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在凝视茫茫湖水之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛蕴含着探求与深邃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是一只普通的船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生了一个伟大的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将生命诞生在水里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才懂得什么是深沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水能载舟也能覆舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了八十年的风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个水上摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜推动搁浅的历史向前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风也罢雨也罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望总悬在船窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔地触摸颠簸的荷香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟和水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在摇篮荡漾的音乐里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻到顽强的生命气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过了冬季和春季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划着两片荷叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两片信仰的荷叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进、斗争、再前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远照耀在成长的过程中"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}